cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper proposes a runway embedding learning model that uses fashion runway images to learn every season's collection embedding. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper designs neural network models to leverage structured fashion runway show data and train RNN/LSTM models to capture the designers' style evolution. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a fashion trend prediction framework that uses machine learning techniques to predict next-season designs. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper uses fashion runway images as input data to train the models. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper involves predicting fashion trends and designs, which can be seen as a form of information retrieval.
